1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 5]

2
00:00:16,815 --> 00:00:17,454
Grandma,

3
00:00:21,615 --> 00:00:22,414
Mo...

4
00:00:22,815 --> 00:00:23,454
How did you

5
00:00:23,855 --> 00:00:25,214
get like this?

6
00:00:26,095 --> 00:00:28,334
This is the truth about how I grew up

7
00:00:28,535 --> 00:00:30,214
under Second concubine's "care"

8
00:00:30,215 --> 00:00:31,614
after my mother died when I was six.

9
00:00:32,215 --> 00:00:33,534
She'd hit me whenever she was upset,

10
00:00:33,615 --> 00:00:35,414
and after every miscarriage,

11
00:00:35,415 --> 00:00:36,894
she'd fly into a rage and unleash a torrent

12
00:00:37,015 --> 00:00:37,774
of abuse at me.

13
00:00:39,015 --> 00:00:39,774
Until..

14
00:00:40,695 --> 00:00:42,094
my brother Zhou Yichen was born.

15
00:00:42,855 --> 00:00:45,134
Only then did she realize I was her only bargaining chip.

16
00:00:46,455 --> 00:00:47,454
Child,

17
00:00:47,775 --> 00:00:49,614
how could it be like this?

18
00:00:51,015 --> 00:00:51,574
All these years,

19
00:00:52,895 --> 00:00:54,014
I never gave up searching

20
00:00:54,015 --> 00:00:56,254
for the truth about Mother's death.

21
00:00:57,495 --> 00:00:58,454
Until a few months ago,

22
00:00:58,455 --> 00:00:59,774
when the nanny who retired from the He residence

23
00:00:59,775 --> 00:01:01,174
finally admitted

24
00:01:01,495 --> 00:01:02,254
that back then, Second concubine

25
00:01:02,255 --> 00:01:03,894
put combustible materials

26
00:01:03,895 --> 00:01:04,694
in the New Year goods sent to my mother.

27
00:01:09,135 --> 00:01:10,494
Mother's accident back then

28
00:01:11,775 --> 00:01:13,574
was deliberately caused by Second concubine

29
00:01:13,575 --> 00:01:14,774
to compete for favor.

30
00:01:15,655 --> 00:01:16,294
Madam!

31
00:01:16,295 --> 00:01:17,374
The house is on fire! Help!

32
00:01:17,655 --> 00:01:18,774
Young master, you can't go in!

33
00:01:19,015 --> 00:01:19,494
Mother!

34
00:01:20,655 --> 00:01:21,494
Save me!

35
00:01:21,775 --> 00:01:22,974
Save me!

36
00:01:22,975 --> 00:01:25,574
Someone save my mother!

37
00:01:25,575 --> 00:01:27,334
Save me!

38
00:01:28,335 --> 00:01:30,574
Save me!

39
00:01:31,015 --> 00:01:33,014
Someone save her!

40
00:01:33,775 --> 00:01:35,254
Mother!

41
00:01:38,815 --> 00:01:40,814
Why did this happen?

42
00:01:41,295 --> 00:01:43,094
Poor child.

43
00:01:43,095 --> 00:01:44,414
My poor daughter.

44
00:01:44,415 --> 00:01:46,414
She was actually killed by her own sister.

45
00:01:46,415 --> 00:01:47,854
Why was she so foolish?

46
00:01:48,935 --> 00:01:50,294
If this is true,

47
00:01:50,735 --> 00:01:51,854
her fate today

48
00:01:52,295 --> 00:01:54,094
is what she brought upon herself.

49
00:01:54,615 --> 00:01:55,494
Zhou Huaiqian!

50
00:01:56,095 --> 00:01:56,614
Mom.

51
00:01:58,015 --> 00:01:59,614
I only ask one thing of you.

52
00:02:00,215 --> 00:02:00,854
Tell me.

53
00:02:01,855 --> 00:02:02,614
In the future,

54
00:02:03,415 --> 00:02:04,534
treat my grandson

55
00:02:04,935 --> 00:02:06,894
as your own child.

56
00:02:07,215 --> 00:02:08,214
Rest assured, Mother.

57
00:02:08,575 --> 00:02:09,854
The He and Zhou families

58
00:02:10,575 --> 00:02:11,734
are one family

59
00:02:12,335 --> 00:02:14,414
I hope you truly think so.

60
00:02:15,535 --> 00:02:16,334
Trust me.

61
00:02:27,375 --> 00:02:29,334
That's the dress the female ghost wore that night!

62
00:02:29,535 --> 00:02:31,014
Why was it with the second young master?

63
00:02:31,495 --> 00:02:32,174
Father!

64
00:02:32,695 --> 00:02:33,334
Grandma!

65
00:02:33,575 --> 00:02:35,494
I found this red robe under the floorboards

66
00:02:35,575 --> 00:02:36,694
in Second concubine's room.

67
00:02:36,815 --> 00:02:38,374
This proves the ghost incidents

68
00:02:38,495 --> 00:02:39,734
were orchestrated by Second concubine!

69
00:02:45,495 --> 00:02:46,134
Brother!

70
00:02:46,695 --> 00:02:47,694
You're late.

71
00:02:48,095 --> 00:02:48,814
A wasted effort.

72
00:02:50,135 --> 00:02:52,454
Fifth Concubine is young and beautiful.

73
00:02:52,575 --> 00:02:54,934
And she's about their age.

74
00:02:55,215 --> 00:02:56,934
They're all rushing to help her.

75
00:02:56,935 --> 00:02:59,294
She's very cunning.

76
00:03:07,575 --> 00:03:07,974
Yimo.

77
00:03:08,215 --> 00:03:10,894
Take care of Dr. Sun Quietly.

78
00:03:11,095 --> 00:03:11,534
Yes.

79
00:03:11,655 --> 00:03:12,414
Take him away.

80
00:03:12,895 --> 00:03:13,814
Fifth concubine, you barged into

81
00:03:14,015 --> 00:03:16,094
Second concubine room recklessly.

82
00:03:16,735 --> 00:03:17,814
so you'll be punished

83
00:03:18,335 --> 00:03:19,974
by sweeping the backyard for three days.

84
00:03:20,735 --> 00:03:21,454
Yes.

85
00:03:21,695 --> 00:03:22,454
Master.

86
00:03:25,815 --> 00:03:26,574
Zhou Yichen.

87
00:03:27,535 --> 00:03:28,334
Father.

88
00:03:28,615 --> 00:03:30,654
You've been acting recklessly lately.

89
00:03:31,535 --> 00:03:32,334
Return to your room

90
00:03:32,855 --> 00:03:34,174
and reflect on your actions.

91
00:03:36,655 --> 00:03:37,574
Yes.

92
00:03:41,815 --> 00:03:43,174
What a masterful scheme.

93
00:03:44,575 --> 00:03:46,574
You let Lan'er see you taking me away,

94
00:03:46,855 --> 00:03:48,334
making me the prime suspect

95
00:03:48,335 --> 00:03:49,534
in Second concubine' burning death.

96
00:03:49,695 --> 00:03:50,933
Then you used this to expose

97
00:03:50,934 --> 00:03:53,254
her past misdeeds of drugging Master.

98
00:03:53,695 --> 00:03:55,734
And clear my arson suspicion.

99
00:03:56,095 --> 00:03:57,334
Leveraging the He family's influence

100
00:03:57,855 --> 00:03:58,933
to pressure Master,

101
00:03:59,455 --> 00:04:01,214
securing your position here.

102
00:04:04,255 --> 00:04:05,134
Now,

103
00:04:05,455 --> 00:04:07,334
am I qualified to protect you?

104
00:04:08,135 --> 00:04:09,654
I didn't expose your ghost scheme,

105
00:04:10,895 --> 00:04:12,094
so we're even.

106
00:04:13,375 --> 00:04:14,374
Don't get any

107
00:04:15,255 --> 00:04:16,254
other ideas.

108
00:04:17,375 --> 00:04:18,094
It seems,

109
00:04:18,575 --> 00:04:19,454
besides Second concubine,

110
00:04:20,575 --> 00:04:21,734
you have other targets.

111
00:04:23,695 --> 00:04:24,933
I don't understand what you're saying.

112
00:04:30,175 --> 00:04:30,654
Xiaoman.

113
00:04:30,815 --> 00:04:32,094
So instead of rehearsing at the drama club,

114
00:04:32,295 --> 00:04:33,574
you've been reading this?

115
00:04:33,695 --> 00:04:34,094
Look,

116
00:04:34,695 --> 00:04:36,494
Wu county has a hero who destroys opium.

117
00:04:36,975 --> 00:04:39,134
They say he wears a Zhong Kui mask

118
00:04:39,335 --> 00:04:40,254
and all-black clothing.

119
00:04:41,135 --> 00:04:42,134
He goes straight to the docks

120
00:04:42,215 --> 00:04:43,974
to destroy ships smuggling opium.

121
00:04:44,335 --> 00:04:45,214
He's incredible!

122
00:04:55,455 --> 00:04:56,574
You're the hero who destroys opium!

123
00:04:57,015 --> 00:04:58,454
Save me!

124
00:04:59,175 --> 00:05:00,174
Datao, he is injured!

125
00:05:00,215 --> 00:05:01,294
Go find Teacher Anna quickly!

126
00:05:01,335 --> 00:05:01,574
Hurry!

127
00:05:01,775 --> 00:05:02,174
Okay.

128
00:05:07,535 --> 00:05:08,294
Did you see a

129
00:05:08,295 --> 00:05:09,454
wounded man come in?

130
00:05:11,655 --> 00:05:12,294
Yes.

131
00:05:13,775 --> 00:05:14,774
He ran out the main gate.

132
00:05:15,215 --> 00:05:15,734
Let's go.

133
00:06:04,135 --> 00:06:05,134
You're awake.

134
00:06:06,855 --> 00:06:07,494
Great.

135
00:06:13,095 --> 00:06:14,654
That was my first kiss.

136
00:06:18,135 --> 00:06:18,974
No, no, not that.

137
00:06:19,495 --> 00:06:21,494
I wasn't trying to take advantage of you.

138
00:06:22,495 --> 00:06:24,374
I was giving you artificial respiration.

139
00:06:24,375 --> 00:06:25,374
I'm here to save you.

140
00:06:26,935 --> 00:06:27,574
Thanks.

141
00:06:28,575 --> 00:06:30,134
Thank you for saving me.

142
00:06:32,135 --> 00:06:32,894
I recognize you

143
00:06:33,935 --> 00:06:35,014
Hero who destroys opium..

144
00:06:37,215 --> 00:06:37,934
He's been shot.

145
00:06:38,095 --> 00:06:38,934
Careful.

146
00:06:46,935 --> 00:06:48,454
Forcing you to leave here

147
00:06:49,575 --> 00:06:51,094
was to protect you.

148
00:07:10,815 --> 00:07:11,574
Don't be so hard

149
00:07:11,575 --> 00:07:12,934
on yourself trying to live up to

150
00:07:12,935 --> 00:07:14,214
others' expectations.

151
00:07:15,455 --> 00:07:17,214
Not only will I not tell anyone,

152
00:07:17,695 --> 00:07:18,814
but I'm also looking forward

153
00:07:18,935 --> 00:07:20,294
to your next creation.

154
00:07:26,455 --> 00:07:27,814
Such skillful hands.

155
00:07:47,935 --> 00:07:48,694
Third concubine.

156
00:07:59,975 --> 00:08:00,574
Chen.

157
00:08:01,415 --> 00:08:02,974
I made you some fungus and lotus seed soup.

158
00:08:03,015 --> 00:08:03,814
Drink it while it's hot.

159
00:08:04,415 --> 00:08:05,214
Thank you, Mother.

160
00:08:05,735 --> 00:08:07,454
Your father values you more now,

161
00:08:07,855 --> 00:08:09,014
and treats me better too.

162
00:08:09,415 --> 00:08:10,534
All my hopes

163
00:08:10,895 --> 00:08:11,934
rest on you.

164
00:08:14,135 --> 00:08:15,014
Don't worry, Mother.

165
00:08:15,895 --> 00:08:16,454
I

166
00:08:17,495 --> 00:08:19,294
will not let Father leave us.

167
00:08:33,975 --> 00:08:34,974
As long as you're obedient.

168
00:08:59,735 --> 00:09:00,894
Master Zhou.

169
00:09:01,415 --> 00:09:04,254
After years of struggle in the underworld,

170
00:09:04,535 --> 00:09:07,694
you've committed too many sins of bloodshed.

171
00:09:08,215 --> 00:09:10,254
You need to purge it all

172
00:09:10,375 --> 00:09:14,854
to return to your youthful state.

173
00:09:14,935 --> 00:09:16,534
That's good.

174
00:09:16,935 --> 00:09:19,094
Give me a little more time,

175
00:09:21,135 --> 00:09:25,654
and I'll return to my youth.

176
00:09:54,655 --> 00:09:55,334
Master Zhou.

177
00:09:56,735 --> 00:09:57,974
Based on the evidence at the scene

178
00:09:57,975 --> 00:09:59,814
and the autopsy report,

179
00:10:00,175 --> 00:10:03,174
her death appears to have been accidental-

180
00:10:03,495 --> 00:10:04,734
opium smoking indoors

181
00:10:04,895 --> 00:10:07,334
triggered a fatal fire.

182
00:10:07,935 --> 00:10:08,814
Give it to me.

183
00:10:12,695 --> 00:10:13,854
We reached this conclusion

184
00:10:14,135 --> 00:10:14,854
for three reasons!

185
00:10:15,015 --> 00:10:16,134
Alright.

186
00:10:16,695 --> 00:10:17,454
I understand.

187
00:10:19,415 --> 00:10:20,854
Thank you for your trouble, Captain Yu.

188
00:10:21,655 --> 00:10:23,054
It's no big deal.

189
00:10:23,495 --> 00:10:24,814
Wrap up the case quickly.

190
00:10:26,135 --> 00:10:27,894
Give our regards to the Director.

191
00:10:29,095 --> 00:10:29,734
See him out.

192
00:10:30,735 --> 00:10:31,374
Goodbye.

193
00:10:32,975 --> 00:10:34,494
This way, Captain Yu.

194
00:10:36,895 --> 00:10:37,374
By the way

195
00:10:38,695 --> 00:10:39,854
there's one thing.

196
00:10:40,375 --> 00:10:41,374
I've been meaning to ask you.

197
00:10:42,375 --> 00:10:43,214
Go ahead, Father.

198
00:10:44,215 --> 00:10:46,494
Does He family have a mysterious mastermind?

199
00:10:48,215 --> 00:10:48,934
I've heard of it,

200
00:10:50,215 --> 00:10:53,014
but I've never seen them at the He residence.

201
00:10:53,375 --> 00:10:54,574
Grandmother never mentioned it either.

202
00:10:56,895 --> 00:10:58,454
Because your grandmother

203
00:10:59,615 --> 00:11:00,974
is guarding against me.

204
00:11:02,295 --> 00:11:03,574
Are you suggesting

205
00:11:03,895 --> 00:11:05,294
that I should investigate it?

206
00:11:11,815 --> 00:11:12,614
Yimo.

207
00:11:13,135 --> 00:11:14,294
After all, you bear the Zhou surname.

208
00:11:14,375 --> 00:11:16,374
As long as you prove to me

209
00:11:16,895 --> 00:11:18,014
your loyalty,

210
00:11:18,575 --> 00:11:20,574
the future Zhou family estate

211
00:11:20,615 --> 00:11:23,214
could very well fall into your hands.

212
00:11:24,895 --> 00:11:26,374
When it comes to vision,

213
00:11:26,495 --> 00:11:27,654
one must look far ahead.

214
00:11:27,935 --> 00:11:28,694
Do you understand?

215
00:11:28,855 --> 00:11:29,534
Understood.

216
00:11:30,575 --> 00:11:31,854
I know what to do, Father.

217
00:11:50,335 --> 00:11:50,814
Xiaoman.

218
00:11:59,975 --> 00:12:00,574
Captain Yu.

219
00:12:01,295 --> 00:12:01,974
Have some respect!

220
00:12:04,295 --> 00:12:05,454
Or I'll call for help.

221
00:12:17,455 --> 00:12:18,454
Three years

222
00:12:19,935 --> 00:12:21,294
I've been searching for you for three years.

223
00:12:22,415 --> 00:12:23,574
No trace of you anywhere.

224
00:12:24,455 --> 00:12:25,454
I thought you were dead.

225
00:12:28,535 --> 00:12:30,014
Do you know how I've lived these three years?

226
00:12:35,415 --> 00:12:36,774
I'm sorry to disappoint you, Captain Yu.

227
00:12:38,015 --> 00:12:39,534
Until I uncover the truth,

228
00:12:40,295 --> 00:12:41,414
I won't die.

229
00:12:48,655 --> 00:12:49,414
Xiaoman.

230
00:12:50,135 --> 00:12:51,454
The Zhou family holds immense power.

231
00:12:51,455 --> 00:12:52,814
Their connections are intricate.

232
00:12:53,415 --> 00:12:54,174
It's not simple

233
00:12:54,855 --> 00:12:55,934
Stay out of this mess.

234
00:12:56,135 --> 00:12:56,654
Come with me.

235
00:12:56,815 --> 00:12:57,854
Are you any simpler?

236
00:13:00,575 --> 00:13:01,734
Don't think I'm still that naive girl

237
00:13:01,735 --> 00:13:02,694
from back then.

238
00:13:04,175 --> 00:13:05,774
How did you become Captain?

239
00:13:06,775 --> 00:13:08,654
Didn't you step over my sister's corpse

240
00:13:08,655 --> 00:13:10,014
to climb step by step?

241
00:13:10,295 --> 00:13:11,694
I had no choice back then.

242
00:13:12,135 --> 00:13:13,694
If you had insisted on uncovering the truth,

243
00:13:13,975 --> 00:13:15,414
the Zhou family would have silenced you.

244
00:13:16,575 --> 00:13:18,174
The police would have covered up the truth.

245
00:13:18,975 --> 00:13:20,294
All crows are black under the sun.

246
00:13:20,975 --> 00:13:22,174
Everyone operates this way.

247
00:13:25,575 --> 00:13:26,294
You don't understand.

248
00:13:27,295 --> 00:13:28,014
I wanted to protect you.

249
00:13:28,015 --> 00:13:28,574
I know that.

250
00:13:29,935 --> 00:13:32,014
For the sake of our past relationship,

251
00:13:32,575 --> 00:13:33,534
please stop hindering me.

252
00:13:42,135 --> 00:13:43,214
Do you still carry

253
00:13:44,335 --> 00:13:45,174
the gun I gave you?

254
00:13:45,855 --> 00:13:46,454
Why?

255
00:13:46,815 --> 00:13:47,574
You want it back?

256
00:13:48,975 --> 00:13:49,614
Of course not.

257
00:13:50,415 --> 00:13:51,814
Keeping it protects you.

258
00:13:52,215 --> 00:13:52,854
That reassures me.

259
00:13:55,735 --> 00:13:56,814
If you encounter trouble,

260
00:13:57,615 --> 00:13:58,334
find me anytime.

261
00:14:00,215 --> 00:14:01,334
Having a patrol captain as a friend

262
00:14:03,815 --> 00:14:05,094
makes things easier.

263
00:14:22,535 --> 00:14:23,454
It's so late.

264
00:14:23,575 --> 00:14:24,534
What are you doing here?

265
00:14:26,495 --> 00:14:28,014
I saw your door was open,

266
00:14:28,015 --> 00:14:29,334
so I came in impulsively.

267
00:14:29,815 --> 00:14:31,614
I wanted to give you a gift.

268
00:14:33,415 --> 00:14:34,774
I made it myself.

269
00:14:37,815 --> 00:14:38,774
This is me?

270
00:14:41,815 --> 00:14:42,974
Then I can't accept it.

271
00:14:45,895 --> 00:14:47,014
Didn't you say,

272
00:14:47,935 --> 00:14:49,214
one should persevere

273
00:14:49,575 --> 00:14:50,814
in something they love?

274
00:14:50,815 --> 00:14:51,854
I did say that.

275
00:14:52,895 --> 00:14:53,174
But...

276
00:14:53,175 --> 00:14:54,214
Don't get me wrong.

277
00:14:55,375 --> 00:14:56,414
I just wanted to give you

278
00:14:56,695 --> 00:14:59,814
this gift that I carved myself.

279
00:15:02,695 --> 00:15:03,974
You won't accept it?

280
00:15:05,495 --> 00:15:06,134
Second Young Master.

281
00:15:08,495 --> 00:15:09,734
I'm your dad's concubine.
